Zm_BeachCity_v1 is the name of this new Map. This map has over 30 spots and is not to small and not to big. 

- some fun spots
- 48 spawns
- Costum Textures
- Costum Models
- some Secrets
- background sounds

[Here a link for the map video!:)](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RsOM3Mi5Qs&feature=plcp "video")
I hope you have fun on this map.

- If you find some bugs pm me !
- Video for this map is coming !

Comment and rate pls.
